      "$value": "Akzidenz-Grotesk",
      "$type": "fontFamily",
      "$description": "Sole typeface across navigation, body, footer, and brand mark. The weight 400/700 pairing is the entire hierarchy system — no color, no size jumps, no italic to differentiate roles. At 14–15px the grotesk reads as utilitarian editorial; at 20–21px it becomes signage. Normal tracking preserves the geometric, mechanical feel."
    }
